messageBody:
This gets even funnier... My message titled "Last Post" referred to a
message I now find did not get delivered, because I inadvertently sent
it from my business email address which isn't signed on to
Read_Alphabet. It is fascinating how many mistakes one can make without
even trying.

Paige
